{{Quote|There was no time for panic. The dying cannot riot. Those who couldn't make it to here to the med center are dying in their homes. I make the rounds. I do what I can. That is very little.|[[Curi]]|<ref name="Jedi Quest: The Way of the Apprentice">''[[Jedi Quest: The Way of the Apprentice]]''</ref>}}
The '''Isolation Sector''' was the area of the planet [[Radnor/Legends|Radnor]] that was affected by the planet's deadly bioplague. The city-state of [[Aubendo]] was located in the Isolation Sector. The city-state of [[Tacto]] was located in the [[Clear Sector]] when the bioplague first struck [[Aubendo]].

